nodes.text: Cheryl Kallenbach was a Decipher, Inc. employee. According to a Star Wars Customizable Card Game fan site, the character Chyler, featured in the SWCCG expansion set Special Edition Limited, was named after Kallenbach. In addition, the site notes that two other characters named through the SWCCG, Nevar and Nevar Yalnal, were named after Kallenbach's pet dog, Raven.
